msgid ""
"For each pair A - B, tests if A is better predicted as a linear function of "
"B, i.e., l := A ~ 1 + B, or a quadratic function of B, i.e., q := A ~ 1 + B "
"+ B^2.\n"
"    Uses the default settings for Bayesian regression, i.e., a JZS-prior "
"with alpha set to 0.354 and for the model prior a beta binomial distribution "
"with alpha = 1 and beta = 1. Note that since only two models are considered "
"the model prior is equivalent to a uniform model prior."
msgstr ""
"針對每一對 A - B，檢定 A 是否較適合以 B 的線性函數來預測，即 l := A ~ 1 + B，"
"或以 B 的二次函數來預測，即 q := A ~ 1 + B + B^2。\n"
"    採用貝氏迴歸的預設設定，即 JZS 先驗分配，其 alpha 設為 0.354；模型先驗則"
"採用 beta 二項分配，alpha = 1 且 beta = 1。請注意，由於僅考慮兩種模型，此模型"
"先驗等同於均勻模型先驗。"

msgid ""
"Evidence shown in favor of a linear model (l) against a quadratic model (q)."
msgstr "顯示支持線性模型（l）相較於二次模型（q）之證據。"

msgid ""
"Evidence shown in favor of a quadratic model (q) against a linear model (l)."
msgstr "顯示支持二次模型（q）相較於線性模型（l）之證據。"

msgid ""
"The Bernoulli family requires the dependent variable to be a factor with 2 "
"levels."
msgstr "Bernoulli 族要求依變項須為具有 2 個水準之因子。"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The Binomial family requires the weights variable (i.e. total number of "
"trials) to be non-zero."
msgstr "二項式類分析的權重變數（即試驗總數）為需要為整數。"

msgid ""
"The Binomial family requires the dependent variable (i.e. proportion of "
"successes) to be between 0 and 1 (inclusive)."
msgstr "二項式類的分析需要依變數（即成功的比例）介於0和1（含）之間。"

msgid ""
"The Binomial family requires the weights variable (i.e. total number of "
"trials) to be an integer."
msgstr "二項式類分析的權重變數（即試驗總數）為需要為整數。"

msgid ""
"The Gamma family and the Inverse Gaussian family require the dependent "
"variable to be positive."
msgstr "Gamma 族與反 Gaussian 族要求依變項須為正值。"

msgid "The Poisson family requires the dependent variable to be an integer."
msgstr "Poisson 族要求依變項須為整數。"

msgid ""
"The Gaussian family with the log link requires the dependent variable to be "
"positive."
msgstr "Gaussian 族搭配 log 連結函數時，要求依變項須為正值。"

msgid ""
"The Gaussian family requires the dependent variable to be a numerical "
"variable."
msgstr "Gaussian 族要求依變項須為數值變項。"

msgid ""
"Multinomial logistic regression requires the dependent variable to be a "
"factor with at least 3 levels."
msgstr "多項式邏輯斯迴歸要求依變項須為具有至少 3 個水準之因子。"

msgid ""
"Ordinal logistic regression requires the dependent variable to be a factor "
"with at least 3 levels."
msgstr "次序邏輯斯迴歸要求依變項須為具有至少 3 個水準之因子。"

msgid ""
"Firth logistic regression requires the dependent variable to be a factor "
"with 2 levels."
msgstr "Firth 邏輯斯迴歸要求依變項須為具有 2 個水準之因子。"

