msgid ""
"The Wilson model prior corresponds to a beta binomial prior with %1$s = 1 "
"and %2$s = p * %3$s and \n"
"corresponds to an approximate penalization equal to log(%3$s + 1) in log-"
"odds scale for each additional \n"
"covariate added to the model (Consonni et al., 2018; Wilson et al., 2010)."
msgstr ""
"Wilson 模型先驗對應於 β-二項式先驗，其中 %1$s = 1，%2$s = p × %3$s，\n"
"並且在對數勝算尺度下，對每增加一個自變數的模型，對應的近似懲罰為 \n"
"log(%3$s + 1)（Consonni et al., 2018; Wilson et al., 2010）。"

msgid ""
"The Castillo model prior corresponds to a beta binomial prior with %1$s = 1 "
"and %2$s = p^u and is suitable \n"
"for sparse regression when there are more covariates than observations "
"(Castillo et al., 2015)."
msgstr ""
"Castillo 模型先驗對應於 beta 二項先驗，其中 %1$s = 1，%2$s = p^u， \n"
"適用於共變項數多於觀測數之稀疏迴歸（Castillo 等人，2015）。"

